name: full trash
text: Whoa, this trash can is full of valuable items!
Unfortunately, you can't pick them up because an inventory system hasn't been implemented yet.

name: pink npc
text: Hey kid, it's getting late. Probably should get yourself home soon.
What, don't wanna take advice from a weird guy standing between two trash cans?

text: Don't mind me, just waiting for my friend.

name: red npc
text: My bus was supposed to arrive half an hour ago...
